snippet.title: 2002 FIFA World Cup - Official Trailer - GameCube
snippet.description:
Watch the trailer for the game "2002 FIFA World Cup" on Nintendo Gamecube.

2002 FIFA World Cup was developed by TOSE and published by EA Sports.

RELEASE DATES:
North America: April 30th 2002
Europe: May 3rd 2002
Japan: May 2nd 2002 (published by Electronic Arts Victor)

NOTES:
The Japanese version of this game was published by Electronic Arts Victor.
